{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@interface","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSObject","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSObject"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can change the snapshotter’s options at any time and reuse the snapshotter","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for multiple distinct snapshots; however, the snapshotter can only generate one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"snapshot at a time. If you need to generate multiple snapshots concurrently,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"create multiple snapshotter objects.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For an interactive map, use the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"type":"text","text":" class. Both "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"type":"text","text":" are compatible with offline packs managed by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},